---
import BaseLayout from '../../../components/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../../components/PageHero.astro';
import StatusNotice from '../../../components/StatusNotice.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Golf Tournament" description="Information about the annual Joe Rossi Hall of Fame Golf Tournament fundraiser." canonicalPath="/events/golf-tournament/">
  <PageHero eyebrow="Annual fundraiser" title="JRHOF Golf Tournament" intro="A day on the course for Hall of Fame members, supporters, community partners, and sponsors." />
  <section class="section"><div class="container grid grid-2">
    <article class="surface"><h2>Play, connect, support</h2><p>The tournament supports the Hall of Fame mission while giving the community a relaxed day to reconnect and recognize its sponsors.</p><h3>Future registration needs</h3><ul><li>Golfer and team contact information</li><li>Foursome members</li><li>Playing and meal selections</li><li>Sponsor package and signage details</li></ul></article>
    <article class="surface"><StatusNotice title="Registration workflow pending"><p>The audited 2026 event information requires date and availability confirmation. No stale external registration link is presented as current.</p></StatusNotice><p>Native tournament registration, sponsor selections, and Stripe Checkout are outside this phase.</p><div class="button-row"><span class="button button-disabled" aria-disabled="true">Registration coming later</span><a class="button button-secondary" href="/sponsor/">Sponsorship information</a></div></article>
  </div></section>
</BaseLayout>
